# Project Demonstration

## Project Title

Voice-Based Concept Understanding Analyzer (VBCUA)

## Demonstration Overview

This demonstration showcases the complete workflow of the Voice-Based Concept Understanding Analyzer.

The application accepts a student's spoken explanation as input, converts the speech into text using OpenAI Whisper, compares it with a reference answer using Sentence Transformers, calculates a concept understanding score, generates personalized feedback, and creates a downloadable PDF assessment report.

## Demonstration Steps

1. Launch the Streamlit application.
2. Upload an audio file (WAV, MP3, or M4A).
3. Select or load the reference answer.
4. Click the Analyze button.
5. View the generated transcript.
6. Observe the similarity score, grade, and feedback.
7. Download the generated PDF report.

